H0.text: Pulley is the simple machine used when a softball bat hits a softball.

H1.text: Lever is the simple machine exemplified by using a softball bat to hit a softball.

H2.text: An inclined plane is the simple machine exemplified by using a softball bat to hit a softball.

H3.text: Wheel and axle is the simple machine exemplified by using a softball bat to hit a softball.
